      "agent_instructions": "Read all `.changesets/*.yaml` files accumulated on **main** since the last release tag, under the project's changeset directory, via the _changeset.read_changesets Tool. On a trunk there is no release branch — the changesets live on main and the release bumps main in place. Return the parsed list. An empty list is the legitimate no-release-needed terminal state — do not force a release when nothing is pending.",
