      "agent_instructions": "Composite Step using two Tools in sequence: (1) _changeset.cumulative_tier reduces the pending changesets to the highest tier (major dominates minor dominates patch); (2) _changeset.next_version applies that tier to the current version per SemVer. The Step's tool_ref points at cumulative_tier (the primary); next_version follows immediately in the imperative path. Return both intermediate and final values.",
