      "agent_instructions": "Commit the bumped version-files + updated CHANGELOG.md as a single Conventional Commit (chore(release): v<next-version>) **directly to main** (no promotion PR — this is the trunk model). Author identity MUST be set to github-actions[bot]: it is the bot-authored marker the loop-guard regex uses on subsequent cycles to skip its own release commit and prevent the release-of-release loop (#132). Author identity is load-bearing.",
